  <h1>Privacy</h1>

  <p>
    This site deliberately avoids any data processing beyond what is technically
    necessary to operate it.
  </p>

  <h2>No cookies, no tracking, no ads</h2>
  <p>
    This documentation site sets no cookies, embeds no analytics or tracking
    services and shows no ads. No profiles are built and no personal data is
    passed to third parties.
  </p>

  <h2>Server logs</h2>
  <p>
    When the pages and the API are accessed, the hosting produces technically
    necessary server logs (for example IP address, time of the request, requested
    resource, user agent). This data serves secure and stable operation and the
    prevention of abuse. Operation takes place on a server in Germany. This data
    is not combined with other data sources.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you contact me by email, I process the transmitted data solely to handle
    your request. Contact:
    <a href="mailto:admin@infranode.dev">admin@infranode.dev</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights under the GDPR</h2>
  <p>
    You have the rights to information, rectification, erasure, restriction of
    processing, data portability and objection. You also have the right to lodge a
    complaint with a data protection supervisory authority. For any request, reach
    me at <a href="mailto:admin@infranode.dev">admin@infranode.dev</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Controller</h2>
  <p>
    The controller for the processing is Khaled Cherif. The full provider details
    are in the <a href="/en/imprint/">Imprint</a>.
  </p>
</Docs>
